title: Bonjour Tristesse OST (1958) Georges Auric - Jean Seberg
description:
Bonjour Tristesse (1958) Otto Preminger

Music by Georges Auric

This fifty year old (!) piece of vinyl clearly has individual tracks, but the sleeve and label provide no cue titles! The cover only mentions that the record contains the "themes" from the film. So I just numbered them, adding Juliette Greco whenever 
she sings.

02 - Bonjour Tristesse Theme #2 (Juliette Greco)
